    {
      "start": 288.21,
      "end": 289.73,
      "text": "자, 오늘 장면 듣고 올게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.35,
      "end": 294.39,
      "text": "Then there was a big reunion at his 60th birthday."
    },
    {
      "start": 294.69,
      "end": 296.97,
      "text": "Ingrid had persuaded him to invite everybody."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.53,
      "end": 302.19,
      "text": "Ingrid was adamant about reconstructing Bergman's relationship with his family."
    },
    {
      "start": 303.64,
      "end": 311.6,
      "text": "So, do you think you can create a great body of work and raise a family at the same time?"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.6,
      "end": 313.14,
      "text": "A body of work of that scope?"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.14,
      "end": 316.92,
      "text": "At the age of 42, Bergman had directed 25 films."
